ens flare同compression 之前zeiss出左幾支anamorphic 都因為出黎既footage太完美無人用 Zeiss要出個Flare Set 加返啲flare同reduce sharpness</blockquote>"},{"pid":"235db8fadb2a01aa6116d6a0915b5f23d7335101","tid":161724,"uid":39750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T08:26:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係anamorphic lens既鏡片結構影響</blockquote><br />\n橫掂都係用ARRI XT拍, 點解唔用新鏡拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> breathing 又冇咁勁 又多選擇, 點解仲要用Panavision 啲老鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為舊anamorphic 電影<em>感</em>重 好多導演同cinematography都好喜歡 anamorphic 既變形lens flare同compression 之前zeiss出左幾支anamorphic 都因為出黎既footage太完美無人用 Zeiss要出個Flare Set 加返啲flare同reduce sharpness</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qmd5m4gB9yw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dqmd5m4gB9yw&d=beIwg85N8Ddzcl6rIyS0GZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=5f0fe997\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qmd5m4gB9yw</a><br />\n呢條片講解左好多乜野anamorphic 點解啲人會用佢地"},{"pid":"f4a8b7232a8222bade2300e8b7c166372517fa02","tid":161724,"uid":51767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T08:49:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係anamorphic lens既鏡片結構影響</blockquote><br />\n橫掂都係用ARRI XT拍, 點解唔用新鏡拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> breathing 又冇咁勁 又多選擇, 點解仲要用Panavision 啲老鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為舊anamorphic 電影<em>感</em>重 好多導演同cinematography都好喜歡 anamorphic 既變形lens flare同compression 之前zeiss出左幾支anamorphic 都因為出黎既footage太完美無人用 Zeiss要出個Flare Set 加返啲flare同reduce sharpness</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qmd5m4gB9yw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dqmd5m4gB9yw&d=beIwg85N8Ddzcl6rIyS0GZZgE6vMW1KEzM